      • add

        public void add(Entity<?>... entities)
        Adds the given Entity instances to this Group.

        The entities will be displayed within a container controlled by this Group.

        Parameters:
        entities - the Entity instances to be added to this group.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if at least one given Entity is already in a Group.
